### CustomService API Tests

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create Resource
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "specs": {
    "name": "server-01",
    "type": "virtual-machine",
    "cpu_cores": 4,
    "memory_gb": 16,
    "region": "us-east-1",
    "tags": ["production", "web-server"]
  }
}

###

### List All Resources
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Resource by ID (replace {resource-id} with actual ID from create response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources/{resource-id}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Update Resource (replace {resource-id} with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources/{resource-id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "specs": {
    "name": "server-01-updated",
    "type": "virtual-machine",
    "cpu_cores": 8,
    "memory_gb": 32,
    "region": "us-west-1",
    "tags": ["production", "web-server", "scaled-up"]
  }
}

###

### Delete Resource (replace {resource-id} with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources/{resource-id}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create Sample Storage Resource
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "specs": {
    "name": "storage-bucket-01",
    "type": "object-storage",
    "size_gb": 1000,
    "encryption": true,
    "redundancy": "multi-az"
  }
}

###

### Create Sample Network Resource
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/resources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "specs": {
    "name": "vpc-main",
    "type": "virtual-network",
    "cidr": "10.0.0.0/16",
    "subnets": [
      {
        "name": "public-subnet",
        "cidr": "10.0.1.0/24"
      },
      {
        "name": "private-subnet", 
        "cidr": "10.0.2.0/24"
      }
    ]
  }
}